Explore Microsoft sentinel workbooks (Dashboards)

Microsoft Sentinel comes with what we call "Workbooks." A workbook is a query that visualizes the data and places them into a dashboard. This powerful query language is also used to develop Sentinel Workbooks.

  • Head to Workbooks
  • Click on the My workbooks tab
  • Click on CyberDefenders Workbook Demo
  • Then press on View saved workbook button
